<div class="content" name="FlatUIDArray_r" uuid="a816e3a0-0da7-4140-b394-a32b47bad2cd"><p>The FlatUIDArray_r structure encodes an array of <a href="09f5370d-05ee-459e-903a-4e63e1928169" data-linktype="relative-path">FlatUID_r</a> data structures.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct _FlatUIDArray_r {
   [range(0,100000)] DWORD cValues;
   [size_is(cValues)] FlatUID_r** lpguid;
 } FlatUIDArray_r;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>cValues:</b>  The number of FlatUID_r
structures represented in the FlatUIDArray_r structure. This value MUST NOT
exceed 100,000.</p><p><b>lpguid:</b>   The FlatUID_r data
structures.</p></div>